title: r/Choosingbeggars Buy Me a New Phone! It'd BETTER Be iPhone 11!
description:
r/Choosingbeggars This completely delusional choosing beggar seems to believe that strangers on the Internet should buy her a brand new iPhone 11. The crazy thing is that somebody actually agrees to send her an older model iPhone. But what does she do? She insults them! Lady, a free phone is a free phone. Why on earth would you turn that down when you don't have a phone at all? If you like this video and you want to see more, hit that subscribe button for daily Reddit videos!

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4cHkznpehd0
